    (3,'Computer Science and Economics','technology privacy change','Library Privacy in Practice: System Change and Challenges','Gangadharan, Seeta Pena','A Journal of Law and Policy for the Information Society','Gangadharan, Seeta Pena. “Library Privacy in Practice: System Change and Challenges.” I/S: A Journal of Law and Policy for the Information Society, no. Issue 1, 2016, p. 175. EBSCOhost, search.ebscohost.com/login.aspx?direct=true&db=edshol&AN=edshol.hein.journals.isjlpsoc13.11&site=eds-live.',NULL,'http://eds.a.ebscohost.com/eds/SmartLink/OpenIlsLink?sid=2943ea5b-1d84-42f4-9663-792ab755915a@sessionmgr4008&vid=0&sl=smartlink&st=ilslink_new&sv=sdbn%253Dedshol%2526pbt%253DAcademic%2520Journal%2526issn%253Dgplgroup%2526ttl%253DI%25252FS%25253A%252520A%252520Journal%252520of%252520Law%252520and%252520Policy%252520for%252520the%252520Information%252520Society%2526stp%253DC%2526asi%253DY%2526ldc%253D%2526lna%253DSFX%252520Link%252520Resolver%252520%252528all%252520content%252529%252520%252528EDS%252520Link%252529%2526lca%253DfullText%2526lo%255Fan%253Dedshol%25252Ehein%25252Ejournals%25252Eisjlpsoc13%25252E11&su=https%3A%2F%2Fucelinks%2Ecdlib%2Eorg%2Fsfx%5Flocal%3Fgenre%3Darticle%26atitle%3DLibrary%2520Privacy%2520in%2520Practice%253A%2520System%2520Change%2520and%2520Challenges%26title%3DI%2FS%3A%20A%20Journal%20of%20Law%20and%20Policy%20for%20the%20Information%20Society%26issn%3Dgplgroup%26isbn%3D%26volume%3D13%26issue%3DIssue%25201%26date%3D20160101%26aulast%3DGangadharan%2C%20Seeta%20Pena%26spage%3D175%26pages%3D175%2D198%26sid%3DEBSCO%3AHeinOnline%3Aedshol%2Ehein%2Ejournals%2Eisjlpsoc13%2E11','None'),
