    (25,'Computer Science and Economics','technology privacy change','Three Years of Change: Recent Court Cases under the Video Privacy Protection Act','King, Chris','DePaul Journal of Art, Technology and Intellectual Property Law','King, Chris. “Three Years of Change: Recent Court Cases under the Video Privacy Protection Act.” DePaul Journal of Art, Technology and Intellectual Property Law, no. Issue 2, 2015, p. 135. EBSCOhost, search.ebscohost.com/login.aspx?direct=true&db=edshol&AN=edshol.hein.journals.dael26.12&site=eds-live.',NULL,'http://eds.a.ebscohost.com/eds/SmartLink/OpenIlsLink?sid=5710b328-de3d-4b7e-a3af-67a6ffc2fef5@sdc-v-sessmgr02&vid=0&sl=smartlink&st=ilslink_new&sv=sdbn%253Dedshol%2526pbt%253DAcademic%2520Journal%2526issn%253D10610553%2526ttl%253DDePaul%252520Journal%252520of%252520Art%25252C%252520Technology%252520and%252520Intellectual%252520Property%252520Law%2526stp%253DC%2526asi%253DY%2526ldc%253D%2526lna%253DSFX%252520Link%252520Resolver%252520%252528all%252520content%252529%252520%252528EDS%252520Link%252529%2526lca%253DfullText%2526lo%255Fan%253Dedshol%25252Ehein%25252Ejournals%25252Edael26%25252E12&su=https%3A%2F%2Fucelinks%2Ecdlib%2Eorg%2Fsfx%5Flocal%3Fgenre%3Darticle%26atitle%3DThree%2520Years%2520of%2520Change%253A%2520Recent%2520Court%2520Cases%2520under%2520the%2520Video%2520Privacy%2520Protection%2520Act%26title%3DDePaul%20Journal%20of%20Art%2C%20Technology%20and%20Intellectual%20Property%20Law%26issn%3D10610553%26isbn%3D%26volume%3D26%26issue%3DIssue%25202%26date%3D20150101%26aulast%3DKing%2C%20Chris%26spage%3D135%26pages%3D135%2D146%26sid%3DEBSCO%3AHeinOnline%3Aedshol%2Ehein%2Ejournals%2Edael26%2E12','None'),
